page.title: 10OUR HOMES
page.content: There are 31 children in class 4,two of them live in public houses:The Holly tree and The Sun.The Holly tree used to be a court room and has a secret passage.Four children live in terraced houses,nineteen in semi_ detached and six in detached houses, Lots of children live on the older estate near each other.Some children live on the new estate near the school which was once a field.Most children live in Englefield Green and only two in Egham.Brian who comes from the States is here for a year while his father is at the university lives in a rented house which was a gardener's cottage.Paul lives in a house which was once a bakery.Shihab comes from Sudan has several homes.He lives in a big house in Virginia Water.Sarah lives in a bungalow on a private estate which her father looks after.
